p_n(x) = c_{n,0}x^n + c_{n,1}x^{n-1} + \cdots c_{n,n}
 p_n (1) = n!\\ \Rightarrow \sum_{k=0}^n c_{n,k} = n!\\ c_{n,n-1}=(n-1)!\\ \Rightarrow \sum_{k=1}^{n-2}c_{n,k} = n!-(n-1)!\\ c_{n,n}=0\\ c_{n,1}=1\\ c_{n,2}=\frac{n(n-1)}{2}\\ c_{n,3} = \frac{1}{24} n(n-1)(n-2)(3n-1) 
